      "description": "A loud, fragrant Roman classic given a modern, smoky twist with charred garlic and a whisper of pimentón.",
      "diet": "Vegetarian",
      "ingredients": [
        {
          "qty": "400g",
          "item": "bronze-cut spaghetti"
        },
        {
